window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Three hot couples. Six naughty gifts. One superyacht cruise. What could go oh so right?</b></p> <p>Lately, I'm closer to my rabbit than I am to my celebrity husband. I mean…I'm a happily married woman, but we never have time to play. I'm dying for some holiday fun.</p> <p>Then, our friends propose a vacation with a nightly game that's not safe for work or neighborly gossip. Like, never. I'll have to move if this racy kitty gets out of the bag.</p> <p>Half of us grew up together, four of us work together… and all of us have feelings for each other. Can opening our marriages (and legs) for one week satisfy our curiosity, or will it open the floodgates… in a good way?</p> <p>Between my famous, dreamy husband, his bad-boy costar, my forbidden friend, and their two gorgeous wives, these spicy scenes are not for the big screen.</p> <p>But just once, doesn't a woman deserve to star in a story like this? Don't we all deserve to choose our happy ending(s)?</p> <p>Yeah, I'm about to set sail on a sea of sin. All aboard?</p> <p><i>From the \"Queen of Spice,\" author Kelly Finley, comes a standalone romance featuring a hot and hilarious group of friends. This steamy friends-to-lovers, forced proximity romantic comedy will surely heat your laughing cheeks. </i>Holiday for Six <i>is a multi-POV romance. For the best experience, you can enjoy this book and then meet all these characters in Finley's other steamy, interconnected stories.</i></p>"; 
